After:
```
$ test/lint/lint-spelling.sh 
src/test/base32_tests.cpp:14: fo  ==> of, for
src/test/base64_tests.cpp:14: fo  ==> of, for
test/functional/rpc_getaddressinfo_label_deprecation.py:7: superceded  ==> superseded
```
